---
## Sample notes for enabling the optional github-link plugin.
##
## The default command metadata already lives in conf/plugins/github-link.yaml.
## To enable github-link for a custom robot:
##
## 1. Add an ExternalPlugins.github-link stanza in custom/conf/robot.yaml.
## 2. Create a github_oauth ParameterSet in custom/conf/robot.yaml.
## 3. Add an IdentityProviders.github entry in custom/conf/robot.yaml.
##
## Future setup-github flows should materialize those robot.yaml changes.
